Of the enchanted cave, where they'll be safe for you. Then we can talk about a happy ending."

With that, the goddess entered the shadowy cave And searched out its recesses while Odysseus Brought everything closer—the gold, the bronze,
The well-made clothes the Phaeacians had given him.
 



